column8: No WT animals died during course of study, hence survival was artificially set to 200 days
All wild type mice lived until the end of the study and were "censored" after 200 days (Denoted by a status of 0). All SOD1 mice died before the end of the study (Denoted by a status of 1)
WT_Vehicle_SID = Wild type mice, single daily dose of vehicle
SOD1_veh_SID = SOD1 mice, single daily dose of vehicle
SOD1_veh_BID = SOD1 mice, double daily dose of vehicle
SOD1_SID_350mg/kg = SOD1 mice, single daily dose of 350 mg/kg compound in males
SOD1_BID_350mg/kg = SOD1 mice, double daily dose of 350 mg/kg compound in males
SOD1_SID_200mg/kg = SOD1 mice, single daily dose of 200 mg/kg compound in females
SOD1_BID_200mg/kg = SOD1 mice, double daily dose of 200 mg/kg compound in females
